 for generation of left isomerism in Ccdc40 mutant embryos.", "year" 2017, "raw_pages" "e0171180", "volume" "12", "ISBN" nil, "PMID" 28182636}, "PUB00086847" {"URL" nil, "issue" "5", "authors" ["Sui W" "Hou X" "Che W" "Ou M" "Sun G" "Huang S" "Liu F" "Chen P" "Wei X" "Dai Y."], "ISO_journal" "Clin Respir J", "DOI_URL" "https://doi.org/10.1111/crj.12268", "medline_journal" "Clin Respir J", "title" "CCDC40 mutation as a cause of primary ciliary dyskinesia: a case report and review of literature.", "year" 2016, "raw_pages" "614-21", "volume" "10", "ISBN" nil, "PMID" 25619595}}, :go-terms [{"identifier" "GO:0035082", "name" "axoneme assembly", "category" {"code" "P", "name" "biological_process"}}], :entry-id nil, :hierarchy {"accession" "IPR037386", "name" "Coiled-coil domain-containing protein 40", "type" "Family", "children" []}, :is-llm false, :entry-annotations {}}}